ray.rage.rendersystem

Interface RenderQueue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Renderable>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GL4RenderQueue

    public interface RenderQueue
extends java.lang.Iterable<Renderable>
    A render queue defines an ordered container for renderables to be submitted to the render-system by the scene-manager.
    Author:
    Raymond L. Rivera
